<H4>Issues & Troubleshooting</H4>

<font size="-1">
<UL>
<LI> The graph browser of ConceptBase requires a Java JRE 1.4 or higher. Unfortunately, Java 6 Update 12 or higher is not
     compatible with the graph browser. You are advised to install Java 5 Update 18 under Linux, Solaris and Windows XP.
     Under Windows Vista, you are advised to use Java 6 Update 7. All these releases can be installed via the
     <A HREF="http://java.sun.com/products/archive/">Java Archive page</A>. Deinstallation of an already installed
     more recent Java should not be necessary but could be enforced by the Java installation routine.
     Windows users can also use the cb72*wjava variant from above. It has a pre-installed local Java 6 Update 7 JRE.
</UL>
</font>

